# Cloudflare Pages security headers (Remediation Phase 3 — M2, L6).
# See SECURITY-REVIEW-2026-07-15.md M2/L6 and SECURITY-FIX-PLAN.md Phase 3.
#
# The CSP is built from the ONLY external origins this app legitimately uses:
#   - Google Fonts: fonts.googleapis.com (stylesheet) + fonts.gstatic.com (font files)
#   - Supabase (REST + Storage + Edge Functions over https, Realtime over wss):
#     rpwklsrdfqyisogbcdgg.supabase.co
#   - Embed players (iframes only): YouTube, Vimeo, Loom, SoundCloud
# Dodo checkout is a full-page redirect (not fetch/iframe), so it needs no CSP entry.
#
# script-src is strict 'self' — the former inline theme script now lives in
# /theme-init.js. style-src keeps 'unsafe-inline' because React/Framer/Tiptap/Konva
# set element style attributes at runtime (style injection is low-risk; script
# injection is what the strict script-src blocks).
#
# VERIFY after deploy: open DevTools console on the boards, a note with an embed,
# a canvas with an embed, and after a realtime edit — there should be no CSP
# violation errors, fonts should load, and Supabase REST + WebSocket should connect.
# If a console error names a blocked origin, widen only that one directive.

/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com; font-src 'self' https://fonts.gstatic.com data:; img-src 'self' data: blob: https:; media-src 'self' blob: data: https://rpwklsrdfqyisogbcdgg.supabase.co; connect-src 'self' https://rpwklsrdfqyisogbcdgg.supabase.co wss://rpwklsrdfqyisogbcdgg.supabase.co; frame-src https://www.youtube.com https://player.vimeo.com https://www.loom.com https://w.soundcloud.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; manifest-src 'self'; object-src 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'; upgrade-insecure-requests
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: geolocation=(), interest-cohort=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
